title: '"go install" makes executables globally available.'
pid: 83c74ab3-2972-4d3e-8df4-af0dad9198d3
body: |2-
  Run
    go list -f '{{.Target}}'
  to find Go's "install path".
  Run
    go install
  to put the executable there.
  Add the Go install path to my PATH
  to make everything there globally available.
